Afflictions
	• Weakened: status affliciton, -1d6 damage inflicted by that source 
	• Blind: status affliciton, can't gain benefit from the Instinct stat. 
	• Plagued: status affliction, cannot be if it from their Constitution stat. 
	• Cursed:  
	• Stupefied: status affliction. Can not benefit from their Mind stat. 
	• Broken: status affliction. Cannot benefit from their will stat.  
	• Afraid: status affliction. fearful and unwilling to engage with what frightened them. 
